612
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,100
Milk.

613
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:20,260
- That's right.
- Here comes the milk!

614
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:22,620
So much.

615
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,300
