616
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:25,700
Didn't cost a penny.

617
00:31:25,980 --> 00:31:27,720
This was leftover
from the Cold Beverage Department.

618
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,410
The director said it would be a waste
