00:32:43,540 --> 00:32:44,660
(Dajiang Entertainment City)

636
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:45,700
There was no problem at all.

637
00:32:46,060 --> 00:32:47,020
Look what happened

638
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:47,990
