644
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:56,780
- Here it is, here.
- Here. Here.

645
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:57,620
Tissues. Tissues.

646
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,340
Xiaolu.

647
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:05,180
Bai Lan,

648
00:33:05,180 --> 00:33:06,020
