- Just a lot of people.

653
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:13,860
Three pills each.

654
00:33:15,460 --> 00:33:17,380
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine. I didn't drink it.

655
00:33:17,580 --> 00:33:18,360
Get some cars

656
00:33:18,370 --> 00:33:19,460
