- Get lost. What are you saying?

664
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:31,900
Dumb Jar, take him to the infirmary.

665
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:32,980
Hurry.

666
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,140
