843
00:43:43,740 --> 00:43:44,580
Would I?

844
00:43:50,140 --> 00:43:51,140
It's all been investigated.

845
00:43:51,170 --> 00:43:52,770
The ingredients
that caused the food poisoning

846
00:43:52,790 --> 00:43:54,340
